  "description": "Amethyst Allay and Amethyst Allay Totem to replace the Vanilla Totem",
  "body": "### <center>One of my First Resourcepacks i ever made. Expect Bugs</center><br>\n<center><img alt=\"Heading\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b37e022fd68c8a5e477b90033c0f8ac952fd3a1c.png\"></img></center>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n  \n![Optifine or EMF and ETF Required](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4fee00b0dd5f0baf7e030a067ac1ff89a37fc09f.png)\n\n<center>We use Entity Model Features and Entity Texture Feature to make the Pack work</center>\n<center>IT WILL NOT WORK WITHOUT IT !</center><br>\n<center><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entity-model-features\">[EMF] Entity Model Features</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entitytexturefeatures\">[ETF] Entity Texture Features</a></center><br>\n<center>This texture pack adds an Amethyst Allay and an Amethyst Allay Totem<br>giving you a nicer totem while playing</center><br><br>\n\n> ## How the Totem of Undying Looks\n> \n> ![Totem](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/22577597d77a1f86f72ea89d3d8b3215e9b54f27.png)\n\n> ## How the Amethyst Allay Looks\n> \n> <img alt=\"How the Allay looks\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/83a28ff46c5fa61983700606a8eedf6c91fa4698.png\" hight=\"400\" width=\"400\"></img>\n> \n<br>\n<center>Works with version 1.19 - 26.1 (Current latest Version)</center>\n<center>Because 1.19 is the Version the Allay got added</center>",
